WEBVTT

00:04:29.879 --> 00:04:32.066
to dealing with homeless individuals

00:04:32.090 --> 00:04:33.342
and drug addicts.

00:04:34.486 --> 00:04:36.972
It was called the harm reduction model,

00:04:36.996 --> 00:04:40.609
and it consisted of passing out
clean needles and condoms.

00:04:40.633 --> 00:04:43.341
And I thought, "Now that
is one stupid idea."

00:04:43.365 --> 00:04:44.588
(Laughter)

00:04:44.612 --> 00:04:47.607
"That's just going to encourage them
to continue that behavior.

00:04:47.631 --> 00:04:49.282
Just tell them to stop."

00:04:51.323 --> 00:04:54.317
